            <abstract>
                <label>Abstract</label>
                <p>A new replacement name is proposed for the species <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tropidocephala</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">speciosa</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Ding, 2006 (<tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="order">Hemiptera</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>: <tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="infraorder">Fulgoromorpha</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>: <tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="family">Delphacidae</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>: <tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="tribe">Tropidocephalini</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name>), preoccupied by <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tropidocephala</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">speciosa</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> (Bierman, 1908): <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tropidocephala</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">dingi</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Sun, Yang &amp; Chen, <bold>nom. n.</bold> = <italic><tp:taxon-name><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Tropidocephala</tp:taxon-name-part> <tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="species">speciosa</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> Ding, 2006. The photographs and illustrations of this species are also provided.</p>
            </abstract>
